settings.description: My First Level! So This is a fun level to play. There's also a secret ending by going to the chest. To do this, you have to step on the note blocks, Step on P-switch, and run to the chest.
A nasty short showcasing the unpredictability of chain chomps.  see if you make make it through!
Venture through a switch-and-money-filled world of speedrunning, careful timing, precise jumps, and more! There's also an E-Coin up high in space, waiting to be found!
Careful, these creepy crawling beetles just love roaming around on all these wooden walkways! think you can find their hidden Tanooki suit though?
Test some of your skills with the Tanooki Suit in this brief adventure up in the sky!
Bullets everywhere, and they're all dangerous! either they'll turn back to try to hit you again, or just seek you down for the perfect shot!
